sentences: Rick White (born 5 December 1970) is a Canadian musician and singer-songwriter.
White released his first solo album, The Rick White Album, in late 2005.
He followed it with Memoreaper in 2007.
White's next album, 137, is a double album which was released in 2009 on Blue Fog Recordings.
His latest record, The Opening, released in 2019 was recorded with Eiyn Sof.
